load eQTL and pdQTL tibble for chr 22

eQTL_vs_pdQTL_chr22 = read_csv("../TD20200925/eQTL_vs_pdQTL_chr22.csv", col_types = cols())
rmarkdown::paged_table(eQTL_vs_pdQTL_chr22)
(eQTL_vs_pdQTL_chr22 %>% filter(beta.raw * beta.TD < 0, !is.na(beta.raw), !is.na(beta.TD)) %>% 
   ggplot(aes(beta.raw, beta.TD)) + geom_point()) %>%
  plotly::ggplotly()
